# Extern Resume & Job Search Agent — .gitignore
#
# Purpose: keep candidate's personal data and search tracking out of GitHub. 
# The template structure and example files stay; active runs and profiles stay local.

# --- Personal profiles and stories (NEVER push) ---
library/context/master-cv.md
library/context/positioning.md
library/context/voice/voice-profile.md
library/context/voice/intake/taste-interview.md

# Ignore all stories, but keep the examples:
library/context/stories/*
!library/context/stories/EXAMPLE-*.md

# --- Active job applications (NEVER push) ---
# Ignore everything in workspace/applications/ ...
workspace/applications/*
# ... but keep the structure-bearing example files and folders:
!workspace/applications/README.md
!workspace/applications/tracker.EXAMPLE.md
!workspace/applications/EXAMPLE-meridian-business-analyst/
!workspace/applications/EXAMPLE-vanguard-analyst/

# --- Secrets (NEVER push) ---
.env

# --- Scratch / stress-test artifacts ---
_stress-test/

# --- Build / cache cruft ---
__pycache__/
*.pyc

# --- OS / editor noise ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.obsidian/
